- Leverage Server Components for improved performance and SEO
- Use the `use client` directive sparingly, only for client-specific logic
- Implement route groups for better organization of related routes
- Utilize `generateStaticParams` for dynamic routes to optimize build times
- Implement proper error handling with `error.tsx` and `not-found.tsx`